                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-277-victim2021 t18310908-277-viclabel1418"></join>, and employed in Cheapside; I live in Westmoreland-buildings, City-road. On the 17th of August, about eight o'clock in the evening, I was in <placeName id="t18310908-277-crimeloc1419">Chiswell-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-277-crimeloc1419" type="placeName" value="Chiswell-street"></interp>
